sub_title: Functional Analyst / Mainframes Developer : TATA Consultancy Services / ING Belgium
summary:
Collaboration, adaptability, flexibility, organizing and managing are few key things I am great at.

I am DevOps Engineer (Techno-Functional Analyst, Operation Support & Developer) with 7 years of IT experience in Banking domain(ING Belgium) out of which 4+ yrs I have been working in Belgium.
Worked in :
• Bank Merger project (Record Bank --> ING Belgium)
• Migration of Mainframes applications to cloud
• Risk related topics for the bank to maintain good RISK score
• Profitability Management for the bank
• Audit related activities from National Bank of Belgium for the bank

• Certified Professional Scrum Master I
• Experience of working on Unisys Mainframes 
• Handling of 14 applications in the Finance & Risk department of the bank(Functional Analysis, Development, E2E Testing, Deployments). 
• Having sound understanding of Banking & Financial Domain Applications.
• 4+ years of experience of working in Scrum/AGILE

Project Management and related activities like 
•	Project Planning & scoping, 
•	Effort estimation, 
•	resource estimation, 
•	risk management, 
•	change management, 
•	release management, 
•	configuration management, 

International Teamwork : Netherlands, Belgium
